<I>The subject of O-Ren's blood
and nationality</I>

518
01:01:23,354 --> 01:01:26,024
<I>came up before the council
only once.</I>

519
01:01:26,107 --> 01:01:31,029
<I>The night O-Ren assumed power
over the crime council.</I>

520
01:01:31,112 --> 01:01:33,490
<I>The man who seems bound
and determined</I>

521
01:01:33,573 --> 01:01:36,034
<I>to break the mood
is Boss Tanaka.</I>

522
01:01:36,117 --> 01:01:38,953
<I>And what Boss Tanaka
thinks is... </I>

523
01:01:43,374 --> 01:01:44,793
Boss Tanaka!

524
01:01:44,876 --> 01:01:46,711
What's the meaning of this outburst?

525
01:01:46,795 --> 01:01:48,838
This is a time for celebration!

526
01:01:48,922 --> 01:01:52,217
And what exactly are we celebrating?

527
01:01:53,218 --> 01:01:55,470
The perversion of our illustrious council?

528
01:01:57,305 --> 01:02:00,558
Tanaka, have you gone mad?

529
01:02:00,642 --> 01:02:01,976
I will not tolerate this!

530
01:02:02,060 --> 01:02:04,646
You're disrespecting our sister! Apologize!

531
01:02:05,396 --> 01:02:11,319
Tanaka-San, of what perversion do you speak?

532
01:02:16,157 --> 01:02:18,326
My father...

533
01:02:18,409 --> 01:02:19,577
along with yours,

534
01:02:19,661 --> 01:02:22,122
and along with yours,
started this council.

535
01:02:22,205 --> 01:02:23,623
And while...

536
01:02:23,706 --> 01:02:25,375
you laugh like stupid donkeys...

537
01:02:25,458 --> 01:02:27,377
they weep in the afterlife...

538
01:02:27,961 --> 01:02:29,504
- Shut up!

539
01:02:29,587 --> 01:02:31,840
over the perversion committed today!

540
01:02:32,507 --> 01:02:35,427
Outrageous!

541
01:02:35,510 --> 01:02:37,720
Tanaka, it is you who insults this council!

542
01:02:37,804 --> 01:02:39,097
Bastard!

543
01:02:39,889 --> 01:02:41,224
Fuck face!

544
01:02:41,307 --> 01:02:42,934
Gentlemen.

545
01:02:44,853 --> 01:02:50,525
Tanaka obviously has something on his mind.

546
01:02:52,360 --> 01:02:56,948
By all means, allow him to express it.

547
01:02:57,031 --> 01:03:02,120
I speak, of the perversion done to this
council,

548
01:03:03,621 --> 01:03:05,707
which I love...

549
01:03:05,790 --> 01:03:07,625
more than my own children,

550
01:03:08,418 --> 01:03:13,381
by making a Chinese Jap-American
half breed bitch its leader!

551
01:03:20,263 --> 01:03:23,016
Aah! Aah!

552
01:03:33,651 --> 01:03:40,241
So that you understand how serious I am...

553
01:03:40,325 --> 01:03:42,660
I'm going to say this in English.

554
01:03:42,744 --> 01:03:44,496
Huh!

555
01:03:56,257 --> 01:03:58,676
- As your leader...

556
01:03:58,760 --> 01:04:00,678
I encourage you from time to time,

557
01:04:00,762 --> 01:04:04,766
and always in a respectful
manner, to question my logic.

558
01:04:04,849 --> 01:04:06,101
If you're unconvinced

559
01:04:06,184 --> 01:04:08,645
a particular plan of action
I've decided is the wisest,

560
01:04:08,728 --> 01:04:09,938
tell me so.

561
01:04:10,021 --> 01:04:11,648
But allow me to convince you.

562
01:04:11,731 --> 01:04:13,775
And I promise you,
right here and now,

563
01:04:13,858 --> 01:04:17,403
no subject will ever be taboo.

564
01:04:17,487 --> 01:04:20,782
Except, of course, the subject
that was just under discussion.

565
01:04:23,201 --> 01:04:24,661
The price you pay

566
01:04:24,744 --> 01:04:28,039
for bringing up either
my Chinese or American heritage

567
01:04:28,123 --> 01:04:31,960
as a negative is,
I collect your fucking head.

568
01:04:32,043 --> 01:04:34,421
Just like this fucker here.

569
01:04:36,297 --> 01:04:39,300
Now, if any of you
sons of bitches

570
01:04:39,384 --> 01:04:44,222
got anything else to say,
now is the fucking time!

571
01:04:46,307 --> 01:04:47,892
I didn't think so.

572
01:04:50,728 --> 01:04:54,065
Gentlemen, this meeting is adjourned.

573
01:04:54,149 --> 01:04:56,609
One ticket to Tokyo, please.

574
01:07:31,347 --> 01:07:32,599
<I>Moshi moshi.</I>

575
01:09:08,486 --> 01:09:09,821
Hey!

576
01:09:11,990 --> 01:09:13,616
- Hey, yeah!
- Hey, yeah!

577
01:09:52,614 --> 01:09:54,657
Gogo.

578
01:11:23,204 --> 01:11:25,623
Yeah! Whoo!

579
01:12:08,625 --> 01:12:11,669
You have to say "Yes, yes, yes" to
any selfish demands they make.

580
01:12:11,753 --> 01:12:13,254
They demand ridiculous things.

581
01:12:13,338 --> 01:12:16,007
Shut up - Do you know what would
happen if they heard you?

582
01:12:16,091 --> 01:12:17,092
What's gonna happen?

583
01:12:17,175 --> 01:12:18,551
Did you hear about the Tanaka clan?

584
01:12:18,635 --> 01:12:20,470
You're gonna get your head chopped off.

585
01:12:20,553 --> 01:12:21,971
No, I don't want that.

586
01:13:09,352 --> 01:13:10,895
Yes, it's me.

587
01:13:14,607 --> 01:13:18,069
And if you give us a contact number,
we will get back to you.

588
01:13:33,251 --> 01:13:36,212
Who do you remind me of?

589
01:13:37,255 --> 01:13:39,132
Charlie Brown!

590
01:13:40,258 --> 01:13:42,677
You're right, he does look like
Charlie Brown.

591
01:13:42,761 --> 01:13:44,095
Charlie Brown.

592
01:13:44,179 --> 01:13:45,555
Four pepperoni pizzas.

593
01:13:45,638 --> 01:13:47,474
That's not on our menu...

594
01:13:47,557 --> 01:13:49,559
I don't care, bring them, goddammit!

595
01:13:50,643 --> 01:13:53,646
Hey... hey... Charlie, give me a kiss.

596
01:13:54,981 --> 01:13:57,150
O-Ren Ishii!

597
01:13:58,276 --> 01:14:01,029
You and I have unfinished business!

598
01:15:30,702 --> 01:15:33,455
Charlie Brown, beat it.

599
01:15:41,129 --> 01:15:42,714
Miki.

600
01:16:00,565 --> 01:16:02,692
TEAR THE BITCH APART!

601
01:17:32,657 --> 01:17:38,288
So, O-Ren, any more subordinates
for me to kill?

602
01:17:39,789 --> 01:17:41,666
Hi!

603
01:17:42,751 --> 01:17:44,711
Gogo, right?

604
01:17:45,670 --> 01:17:47,172
Bingo.

605
01:17:47,255 --> 01:17:49,215
And you're Black Mamba.

606
01:17:50,925 --> 01:17:54,554
Our reputations precede us.

607
01:17:55,430 --> 01:17:57,223
Don't they?

608
01:17:58,808 --> 01:18:04,105
Gogo, I know you feel you must
protect your mistress.

609
01:18:05,106 --> 01:18:07,692
But I beg you.

610
01:18:07,776 --> 01:18:09,819
Walk away.

611
01:18:16,159 --> 01:18:18,161
You call that begging?

612
01:18:23,792 --> 01:18:27,128
You can beg better than that.

613
01:20:26,873 --> 01:20:28,083
Aah!

614
01:20:34,047 --> 01:20:34,672
Aah!

615
01:20:37,008 --> 01:20:37,759
Aah!

616
01:21:40,822 --> 01:21:42,782
Is that what I think it is?

617
01:21:42,866 --> 01:21:45,577
You didn't think it was
gonna be that easy, did you?

618
01:21:45,660 --> 01:21:52,959
You know, for a second there,
yeah, I kind of did.

619
01:21:53,835 --> 01:21:55,712
Silly rabbit.

620
01:21:56,212 --> 01:21:57,213
Trix are for...

621
01:21:57,297 --> 01:21:58,381
Kids.

622
01:22:02,343 --> 01:22:03,928
Hyaaaaaaah!

623
01:23:13,665 --> 01:23:14,749
Hyah!

624
01:23:27,929 --> 01:23:30,140
Aaaaaaaaahh!

625
01:23:48,450 --> 01:23:49,534
Aaahh!

626
01:24:56,518 --> 01:24:57,936
Aaaaahhh!

627
01:26:12,552 --> 01:26:13,511
Aaah!

628
01:28:27,187 --> 01:28:31,775
This is what you get
for fucking around with yakuzas!

629
01:28:31,858 --> 01:28:33,735
Go home to your mother!

630
01:29:32,377 --> 01:29:35,213
Those of you lucky enough to still
have your lives...

631
01:29:35,296 --> 01:29:38,049
take them with you!

632
01:29:39,634 --> 01:29:41,136
However...

633
01:29:42,387 --> 01:29:46,474
leave the limbs you've lost.

634
01:29:47,642 --> 01:29:51,146
They belong to me now.

635
01:29:55,608 --> 01:29:58,445
Except you, Sofie!

636
01:29:59,154 --> 01:30:02,323
You stay right where you are.

637
01:30:55,794 --> 01:30:58,296
Your instrument
is quite impressive.

638
01:31:02,717 --> 01:31:04,886
Where was it made?

639
01:31:06,387 --> 01:31:08,056
Okinawa.

640
01:31:09,599 --> 01:31:12,936
Whom in Okinawa made you this steel?

641
01:31:13,853 --> 01:31:16,022
This is Hattori Hanzo steel.

642
01:31:16,106 --> 01:31:17,524
YOU LIE!

643
01:31:25,824 --> 01:31:27,659
Mm-hmm.

644
01:31:29,828 --> 01:31:32,539
Swords however, never get tired.

645
01:31:33,665 --> 01:31:37,293
I hope you've saved your energy.

646
01:31:40,839 --> 01:31:42,590
If you haven't...

647
01:31:43,925 --> 01:31:46,511
you might not last five minutes.

648
01:31:48,513 --> 01:31:50,682
But as last looks go,

649
01:31:51,683 --> 01:31:53,685
you could do worse.

650
01:34:32,302 --> 01:34:36,973
Silly Caucasian girl
likes to play with samurai swords.

651
01:34:39,225 --> 01:34:42,103
You may not be able to fight
like a samurai.

652
01:34:45,231 --> 01:34:48,443
But you can at least die
like a samurai.

653
01:35:18,807 --> 01:35:20,517
Attack me...

654
01:35:21,434 --> 01:35:23,144
with everything you have.

655
01:36:18,032 --> 01:36:20,952
For ridiculing you earlier...

656
01:36:23,413 --> 01:36:25,665
I apologize.

657
01:36:33,965 --> 01:36:35,717
Accepted.

658
01:36:51,691 --> 01:36:53,193
Ready?

659
01:36:57,405 --> 01:36:59,157
Come on.

660
01:37:32,107 --> 01:37:41,408
That really was a Hattori Hanzo sword.

661
01:39:47,283 --> 01:39:48,952
Sofie.

662
01:39:49,744 --> 01:39:51,496
Sofie.

663
01:39:51,579 --> 01:39:53,289
My Sofie.

664
01:39:53,373 --> 01:39:55,708
I'm so sorry.

665
01:39:58,837 --> 01:40:02,215
Please.
Please forgive my betrayal.

666
01:40:02,298 --> 01:40:04,050
No more of that.

667
01:40:04,509 --> 01:40:06,302
But still...

668
01:40:06,386 --> 01:40:08,513
But still nothing.

669
01:40:10,515 --> 01:40:13,893
Except my aching heart
over what she's done

670
01:40:13,977 --> 01:40:16,896
to my beautiful
and brilliant Sofie.

671
01:40:17,939 --> 01:40:20,942
I've kept you alive
for two reasons.

672
01:40:21,025 --> 01:40:23,153
The first reason is information.

673
01:40:23,236 --> 01:40:27,282
Burn in Hell, you stupid, stupid blonde!

674
01:40:27,323 --> 01:40:28,700
Burn in Hell, you stupid, stupid blonde!
I'll tell you nothing.

675
01:40:30,076 --> 01:40:34,205
But I am gonna ask you
questions.

676
01:40:34,289 --> 01:40:38,334
And every time
you don't give me answers,

677
01:40:38,418 --> 01:40:40,920
I'm gonna cut something off.

678
01:40:41,880 --> 01:40:47,719
And I promise you, they will be
things you will miss!

679
01:40:48,470 --> 01:40:50,597
Give me your other arm!

680
01:40:53,099 --> 01:40:57,228
I want all the information
on the Deadly Vipers.

681
01:40:57,312 --> 01:40:58,730
If you had to guess...

682
01:40:58,813 --> 01:41:00,273
What they've been doing.

683
01:41:00,356 --> 01:41:01,691
why she left you alive...

684
01:41:01,775 --> 01:41:03,485
And where I can find them.

685
01:41:03,568 --> 01:41:06,362
what would be your guess?

686
01:41:07,363 --> 01:41:09,991
Guessing won't be necessary.

687
01:41:10,075 --> 01:41:12,160
She informed me.

688
01:41:14,496 --> 01:41:18,124
She said I could keep
my wicked life for two reasons.

689
01:41:19,250 --> 01:41:20,752
As I said before,

690
01:41:20,835 --> 01:41:24,380
I've allowed you to keep your
wicked life for two reasons.

691
01:41:25,507 --> 01:41:30,804
And the second reason is
so you can tell him, in person,

692
01:41:30,887 --> 01:41:34,682
everything that happened
here tonight.

693
01:41:34,766 --> 01:41:38,103
I want him to witness
the extent of my mercy

694
01:41:38,186 --> 01:41:41,773
by witnessing
your deformed body.

695
01:41:41,856 --> 01:41:46,027
I want you to tell him all the
information you just told me.

696
01:41:46,111 --> 01:41:49,155
I want him to know what I know.

697
01:41:49,239 --> 01:41:53,451
I want him to know
I want him to know.

698
01:41:53,535 --> 01:41:55,954
And I want them all to know

699
01:41:56,037 --> 01:42:02,710
they'll all soon be
as dead as O-Ren.

700
01:42:25,608 --> 01:42:31,197
Revenge is never a straight line.

701
01:42:33,908 --> 01:42:35,702
It's a forest.

702
01:42:36,661 --> 01:42:39,873
And like a forest it's easy to lose your way...

703
01:42:40,832 --> 01:42:44,252
to get lost... to forget where you came in.

704
01:42:47,589 --> 01:42:51,426
That woman deserves her revenge.

705
01:42:56,639 --> 01:43:01,102
And we deserve to die.

706
01:43:04,481 --> 01:43:08,443
She must suffer
to her last breath.

707
01:43:21,206 --> 01:43:24,125
How did you find me?

708
01:43:24,209 --> 01:43:25,960
I'm the man.

709
01:43:29,881 --> 01:43:33,301
One more thing, Sofie.

710
01:43:33,384 --> 01:43:38,389
Is she aware her daughter
is still alive?

